      "message": "@ed@tanous.net, updated the commit message, \nAdd required client cert context alongside existing Optional client cert context:\n1. Optional client cert context(existing): SSL_VERIFY_PEER (optional cert) - server.pem\n2. required client cert context(new): SSL_VERIFY_PEER | SSL_VERIFY_FAIL_IF_NO_PEER_CERT - server_bmc.pem\nRoute connections via SNI during TLS handshake:\n- IP address in SNI + authorized in satellite_config.json → mTLS\n- Hostname in SNI or unauthorized IP → HTTPS\n\nClient:\nEnable SNI for IP addresses to support satellite detection.SNI\nextension (RFC 6066 Section 3) enables context selection before\nhandshake completion. IP addresses in SNI are RFC-compliant.",
